      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scuffs, some minor paint fading on the hood, and a few small door dings. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows wear in high-traffic areas, and the air conditioning takes a moment to reach full cooling capacity. Mechanically, it starts and runs reliably, though it will likely need routine maintenance like new brake pads and a tire rotation in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
