    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is an ideal choice for a buyer looking for a reliable daily driver that prioritizes mechanical performance over cosmetic flawlessnes. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, ensuring a dependable commute. Please note that the exterior has some visible wear, including minor scratches and a few small dings consistent with its age, and the interior shows signs of regular use. It is a solid, functional car that has been maintained to stay on the road for years to come.",
