    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly pristine, showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously maintained since day one. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint with a professional-grade ceramic coating, the exterior is absolutely flawless\u2014no stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks. It has been exclusively garage-kept and never driven in inclement weather. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time-capsule' condition; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the dashboard is free of any sun damage, and it still retains that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history with all preventive maintenance performed ahead of schedule. With exceptionally low mileage and a smooth, responsive drivetrain, this car offers a driving experience that is indistinguishable from new. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the most discerning buyer.",
